## Form Layouts

### Two-Column to Single
```css
.form-row {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
}

@media (min-width: 640px) {
  .form-row {
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  .form-row > * {
    flex: 1;
  }
}
```

## Testing Checklist

### Viewport Testing
- [ ] 320px (small mobile)
- [ ] 375px (iPhone)
- [ ] 414px (large mobile)
- [ ] 768px (tablet portrait)
- [ ] 1024px (tablet landscape / laptop)
- [ ] 1280px (desktop)
- [ ] 1920px (large desktop)

### Device Testing
- [ ] iOS Safari
- [ ] Android Chrome
- [ ] Desktop Chrome/Firefox/Safari

### Orientation
- [ ] Portrait mobile
- [ ] Landscape mobile
- [ ] Portrait tablet
- [ ] Landscape tablet
